1.1
log
@Initial revision
@
text
@#	$OpenBSD: GNUmakefile.sysdep,v 1.4 2002/06/10 18:08:59 ho Exp $

#
# Copyright (c) 1999 Niklas Hallqvist.  All rights reserved.
